Daniel J. Travanti https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daniel_J._Travanti 0 Daniel J. Travanti (born Danielo Giovanni Travanti, March 7, 1940) is an American actor best known for his starring role as Captain Frank Furillo in the 1980s television drama Hill Street Blues.
